%20the%20partnership%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-investing-billions-into-chatgpt-creator-openai-partnership-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2410%20billion%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20meant%20Microsoft%20held%20any%20power%20over%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20CMA%20will%20review%20whether%20the%20partnership%20has%20resulted%20in%20an%20acquisition%20of%20control%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20where%20it%20results%20in%20one%20party%20having%20material%20influence%2C%20de%20facto%20control%20or%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20voting%20rights%20over%20another%20entity%20%E2%80%94%20or%20change%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20control%20by%20one%20entity%20over%20another.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20watchdog%20added%20that%20it%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bclosely%20monitoring%26quot%3B%20the%20impact%20of%20such%20partnerships%20in%20AI%20that%20could%20weaken%20competition%20and%20hinder%20the%20development%20or%20use%20of%20foundation%20models.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CMA%20is%20inviting%20parties%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20Microsoft's%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI%20could%20have%20an%20adverse%20effect%20on%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20then%20assess%20if%20it's%20worthy%20of%20a%20probe%20after%20external%20parties%20comment%2C%20a%20process%20that%20occurs%20before%20an%20official%20investigation%20is%20launched.%20Interested%20third%20parties%20have%20until%20January%203%20to%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20their%20views%2C%20per%20the%20partnership%20merger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fcma-cases%2Fmicrosoft-slash-openai-partnership-merger-inquiry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einquiry%20page%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CMA%20said%20the%20tie-up%2C%20through%20Microsoft's%20investment%20and%20provision%20of%20its