s%20to%20do%20all%20it%20can%20to%20minimise%20impact%20on%20civilians%E2%80%9D.%20Asked%20if%20it%20was%20doing%20that%2C%20he%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20worry%20not%20enough%20is%20being%20done%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20response%20is%20not%20proportionate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20possibility%20the%20war%20could%20continue%20for%20weeks%20if%20not%20months%2C%20Sriskandarajah%20said%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20going%20to%20be%20an%20even%20greater%20tragedy%E2%80%9D.%20He%20was%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20the%20conditions%20in%20which%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20living%20and%20the%20danger%20of%20disease%20and%20epidemic.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20conditions%20are%20rife%20for%20a%20public%20health%20disaster.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20only%20given%20you%20a%20precis%20of%20the%20main%20points%20made%20by%20Sriskandarajah.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20the%20interview%20which%20I%20will%20leave%20you%20to%20see%2C%20hear%20and%20find%20out%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FavT8I2UADKA%3Fsi%3DY7qkWyI4FTL0G80H%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702037522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08173120%2FKT-8-Dec-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fresumed-israel-hamas-war-worse-ceasefire-paramount-necessity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhananjayan%20Sriskandarajah%20said%20that%20in%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20political%20imperative%20was%20trumping%20what%20is%20morally%20right.%20He%20added%20that%20political%20courage%20and%20leadership%20around%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20were%20lacking%20internationally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthew