0that%20his%20predecessor%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%2C%20the%20first%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Telangana%2C%20has%20%26quot%3BBihar%20DNA%26quot%3B%2C%20indicating%20he%20was%20a%20better%20choice%20for%20the%20southern%20state%20than%20KCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20DNA%20is%20Telangana.%20KCR's%20DNA%20is%20Bihar.%20He%20belongs%20to%20Bihar.%20KCR's%20caste%20is%20Kurmi.%20They%20migrated%20from%20Bihar%20to%20Vijayanagaram%20and%20from%20there%20to%20Telangana.%20Telangana%20DNA%20is%20better%20than%20Bihar%20DNA%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20had%20reportedly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Bihar's%20ruling%20parties%20are%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJD(U)%20leader%20Neeraj%20Kumar%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20Aaj%20Tak%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20taken%20a%20swipe%20over%20%26quot%3BBihar%20DNA%26quot%3B%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20BJP%20lost%20the%20state%20election%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20Telangana%20DNA%2C%20Bihar%20DNA.%20It%20is%20Hindustan's%20DNA.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Telangana%20leader%20said%20such%20a%20thing.%20What%20do%20they%20think%2C%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20grow%20stronger%20with%20such%20statements%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20told%20Aaj%20Tak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20BJP%20criticised%20Mr%20Reddy's%20comment%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20condemn%20his%20comment%20and%20tell%20him%20to%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20termed%20Mr%20Reddy's%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bvery%20shameful%2C%20divisive%20and%20arrogant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20he%20want%20to%20break%20the%20country%3F%20The%20big%20question%20here%20is%20why%20are%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20silent.%20Why%20has%20Nitish%20Kumar%20not%20said%20anything%20(on%20Mr%20Reddy's%20remarks)%20so%20far%3F%20What%20are%20the%20Congress%20members%20in%20Bihar%20doing%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Prasad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20too%2C%20demanded%20Mr%20Reddy%20to%20apologise.%20%26quot%3BThe%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20kept%20insulting%20Hindu%20dharma%20and%20Sanatana%20dharma.%20Now%20they%20have%20come%20to%20'Bihar%20DNA'.%20Is%20it%20appropriate%20to%20say%20that%20'Telangana%20DNA'%20is%20better%20than%20'Bihar%20DNA'%20and%20make%20such%20comments%20against%20the%20people%20of%20another%20state%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BTiger%20Revanth%26quot%3B%20by%20supporters%2C%20has%20been%20credited%20to%20have%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20Congress's%20victory.%20A%20former%20TDP%20leader%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20switched%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%202017.%20He%20was%20appointed%20Telangana%20Congress%20president%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20led%20a%20spirited%20campaign%20against%20the%20KCR-led%20government%20and%20was%20seen%20leading%20street%20protests%20and%20public%20demonstrations%20over%20a%20host%20of%20issues.%20The%20Congress's%20efforts%20bore%20fruit%20and%20the%20party%20trumped%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702037280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fbf1s86pg_revanth-reddy_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-bihar-dna-comment-telanganas-new-chief-minister-revanth-reddy-faces-pushback-4646311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20raised%20a%20big%20row%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%20as%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Telangana%20with%20his%20%26quot%3BBihar%20DNA%26quot%3B%20comment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww