onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fafter-vijay-varmas-best-actor-win-tamannaah-bhatia-celebrates-his-victory-with-a-special-post-4645726%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fafter-vijay-varmas-best-actor-win-tamannaah-bhatia-celebrates-his-victory-with-a-special-post-4645726%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fafter-vijay-varmas-best-actor-win-tamannaah-bhatia-celebrates-his-victory-with-a-special-post-4645726%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%3A%20From%20Investment%20Banker%20To%20Expelled%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20today%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Parliament's%20ethics%20committee%20in%20the%20'cash%20for%20query'%20case.%20The%20House%20held%20her%20guilty%20of%20sharing%20her%20Parliament%20account%20credentials%20and%20accepting%20gifts%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20asking%20questions%20critical%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20House%20accepts%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20committee%20that%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20conduct%20was%20immoral%20and%20indecent%20as%20an%20MP.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate%20for%20her%20to%20continue%20as%20an%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%20who%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20speak%20during%20the%20heated%20debate%20over%20the%20matter%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20read%20out%20her%20statement%20outside%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BThe%20(parliamentary%20ethics)%20committee%20broke%20every%20rule...%20Tomorrow%2C%20the%20CBI%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20my%20home%20to%20harass%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20Banker%20To%20Politician%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20her%20fiery%20speeches%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20was%20an%20investment%20banker%20before%20she%20joined%20politics.%20She%20left%20her%20position%20as%20vice-president%20at%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20in%20London%20in%202009%20and%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Youth%20Congress%20-%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20was%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20trusted%20aides%20of%20the%20party's%20former%20chief%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20'Aam%20Admi%20ke%20sipahi'%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20brief%20stint%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20she%20joined%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%202010%20and%20was%20offered%20a%20ticket%20from%20Karimpur%20in%202016%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20election%20despite%20much%20criticism%20from%20some%20party%20workers%20describing%20her%20as%20too%20%26quot%3Burbane%26quot%3B.%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20however%2C%20took%20on%20the%20challenge%20and%20successfully%20won%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20the%20urban%20version%20of%20feisty%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20was%20given%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20ticket%20in%202019%20from%20Krisnanagar%20-%20a%20seat%20she%20won%20against%20her%20rival%20Kalyan%20Chaubey%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20appointed%20the%20Goa%20in-charge%20for%20the%202022%20Goa%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20her%20expulsion%20today%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20dubbed%20the%20move%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20country's%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20shame%20for%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20We%20condemn%20the%20way%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20expelled%3B%20the%20party%20stands%20with%20her.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20can't%20defeat%20us%20in%20the%20election%2C%20so%20they%20have%20resorted%20to%20vendetta%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20sad%20day%20and%20the%20betrayal%20of%20Indian%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Cash-For-Query%20Case%20Against%20Mahua%20Moitra'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'cash-for-query'%20charges%20against%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20emerged%20in%20October%20after%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20-%20who%20Ms%20Moitra%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20jilted%20ex%26quot%3B%20-%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20CBI%20and%20forwarded%20a%20copy%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20seeking%20to%20address%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20who%20alleged%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20Parliament%20critical%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20businessman%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20requested%20the%20immediate%20suspension%20of%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20alleging%20she%20shared%20her%20parliamentary%20credentials%20with%20him%20to%20post%20questions%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%20who%20has%20been%20denying%20all%20the%20charges%20against%20her%2C%20admitted%20to%20sharing%20her%20login%20credentials%20with%20the%20businessman%20and%20also%20to%20havig%20received%20some%20gifts%20from%20her%3A%20%26quot%3Bone%20scarf%2C%20some%20lipsticks%20and%20one%20eye%20shadow%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ethics%20Panel%20of%20Parliament%20then%20summoned%20both%20Mr%20Dubey%20and%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20in%20the%20case.%20Ms%20Moitra%20was%20summoned%20soon%20after%20but%20she%20defied%20the%20summons%20while%20also%20demanding%20the%20summons%20to%20cross-examine%20Mr%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20finally%20appeared%20before%20the%20committee%20on%20November%202%20before%20staging%20a%20walkout.%20Six%20out%20of%20ten%20members%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20voted%20to%20adopt%20the%20479-page%20report.%20The%20remaining%20four%20members%2C%20belonging%20to%20opposition%20parties%2C%20registered%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20House%20Friday%20noon.%20Later%20the%20government%20moved%20a%20motion%20seeking%20her%20expulsion%20from%20the%20House%2C%20saying%20her%20continuation%20as%20an%20MP%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Buntenable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702036920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fqjjnqrmk_mahua-moitra-pti_625x300_08_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-from-investment-banker-to-expelled-lok-sabha-mp-4646029%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20today%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Parliament's%20ethics%20committee%20in%20the%20'cash%20for%20query'%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-from-investment-banker-to-expelled-lok-sabha-mp-4646029%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-from-investment-banker-to-expelled-lok-sabha-mp-4646029%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-from-investment-banker-to-expelled-lok-sabha-mp-4646029%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20As%20Revanth%20Takes%20Over%2C%20Once-Fortified%20Official%20Residence%20of%20CM%20Thrown%20Open%20to%20Public%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08164833%2FEffect-17.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20hitherto%20heavily%20fortified%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20public%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%208%2C%20after%20authorities%20removed%20the%20barricades%20and%20layers%20of%20fencing%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20newly-sworn-in%20chief%20minister%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20announced%20earlier%2C%20Reddy%2C%20personally%20heard%20the%20grievances%20of%20the%20people%20and%20took%20representations%20from%20them%20during%20the%20re-instituted%20practice%20of%20%E2%80%98Praja%20Darbar%E2%80%99.%20The%20mass%20grievance%20redressal%20programme%20was%20in%20place%20when%20popular%20leader%20and%20former%20Congress%20chief%20minister%20Y.S.%20Rajashekar%20Reddy%20was%20in%20office%20between%202004%20and%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20campaign%2C%20Reddy%20dubbed%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinaccessible%E2%80%9D%20and%20made%20it%20a%20key%20poll%20issue.%20the%20heavily%20fortified%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20KCR%20stood%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Carrogance%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cinaccessibility%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPragati%20Bhavan%2C%20as%20the%20official%20residence%20was%20called%20under%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20has%20been%20re-christened%20as%20Jyotirao%20Phule%20Praja%20(People%E2%80%99s)%20Bhavan%20by%20the%20new%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20who%20hitherto%20put%20visitors%20of%20the%20official%20building%20to%20several%20security%20checks%20stood%20as%20spectators%20on%20Friday%20morning%20as%20milling%20crowds%20walked%20past%20the%20uniformed%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08170313%2FEffect-19.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08170313%2FEffect-19.jpg%201050w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08170313%2FEffect-19-300x140.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08170313%2FEffect-19-1024x477.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688342%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22489%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECrowds%20at%20Praja%20Bhavan%2C%20Telangana%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20official%20residence%2C%20to%20present%20their%20grievances%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%208%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20N.%20Rahul%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20news%20emerged%20on%20Friday%20morning%20that%20KCR%20suffered%20a%20hip%20bone%20injury%2C%20requiring%20replacement%2C%20due%20to%20a%20fall%20in%20the%20toilet%20at%20his%20farmhouse%20in%20Erravelli%20village%20late%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%20He%20was%20admitted%20to%20Yashoda%20Hospital%20in%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Somajiguda.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20instructed%20senior%20health%20officials%20to%20ensure%20all%20medical%20aid%20to%20his%20predecessor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20chief%20minister%20by%20governor%20Tamilisai%20Soundararajan%20in%20a%20massive%20gathering%20at%20Lal%20Bahadur%20stadium%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20Thursday%2C%20December%207.%20His%20cabinet%20colleagues%20who%20were%20also%20sworn%20in%20included%20Mallu%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%20(deputy%20chief%20minister)%3B%20and%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%2C%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%2C%20Damodar%20Raja%20Narasimha%2C%20D.%20Sridhar%20Babu%2C%20Ponnam%20Prabhakar%2C%20Konda%20Surekha%2C%20Seethakka%2C%20and%20Jupally%20Krishna%20Rao%20as%20ministers.%20The%20ceremony%20was%20attended%20by%20top%20Congress%20leaders%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20swearing-in%2C%20Reddy%20announced%20that%20both%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20secretariat%20would%20be%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20public.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20KCR%20had%20built%20a%20new%20secretariat%20complex%2C%20demolishing%20the%20old%20structure.%20The%20new%20structure%2C%20with%20imposing%20buildings%20and%20domes%2C%20overlooks%20the%20Hussain%20Sagar%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%20to%20Revanth%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20the%20media%20personnel%20gained%20access%20to%20the%20high-security%20sixth%20floor%20of%20the%20building%20for%20the%20first%20time%20for%20a%20post-cabinet%20briefing%20by%20ministers%20D.%20Sridhar%20Babu%20and%20Ponnam%20Prabhakar%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-admin%2Fedit.php%5C%22%3EA%20Small%20Coterie%2C%20Hubris%20and%20Forgetting%20That%20the%20Era%20of%20%E2%80%98Doras%E2%80%99%20Is%20Over%3A%20What%20Hurt%20KCR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Praja%20Bhavan%2C%20three%20kilometres%20away%2C%20people%20gathered%20early%20on%20Friday%2C%20hoping%20for%20the%20redressal%20of%20their%20grievances.%20The%20main%20security%20checkpoint%20which%20is%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20walking%20distance%20was%20closed.%20The%20usual%20frisking%20of%20visitors%20and%20noting%20their%20personal%20details%20was%20done%20away%20with.%20Instead%2C%20several%20help%20desks%20were%20set%20up%20to%20assist%20people%20with%20the%20supply%20of%20paper%20and%20in%20writing%20representations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20himself%20had%20shown%20up%20for%20a%20brief%20while%20and%20left%20to%20the%20secretariat.%20He%20later%20flew%20to%20Delhi%20to%20discuss%20filling%20up%20the%20remaining%20seven%20births%20in%20the%20Cabinet%20with%20Congress%20high%20command.%20So%20far%2C%2011%20Cabinet%20berths%20of%20permitted%2018%20have%20been%20filled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20batches%2C%20people%20were%20allowed%20to%20hand%20over%20their%20representations%20to%20minister%20Seethakka.%20Some%20sang%20songs%20punning%20on%20the%20name%20of%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20and%20some%20gave%20sound%20bytes%20to%20TV%20channels%20expressing%20their%20anger%20against%20the%20former%20chief%20minister.%20Most%20of%20the%20representations%20had%20to%20do%20with%20land%20disputes%2C%20employment%2C%20ration%20cards%2C%20government%20housing%2C%20and%20other%20welfare%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08165916%2FEffect-18.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08165916%2FEffect-18.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08165916%2FEffect-18-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08165916%2FEffect-18-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETelangana%20minister%20Seethakka%20receives%20representations%20from%20people%20during%20the%20grievance%20redressal%20programme%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%208%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Twitter%2F%40revanth_anumula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20showed%20up%20to%20submit%20their%20representations%20was%20a%20visually%20impaired%20person%20from%20LB%20Nagar%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Kothakinda%20Raghavender%2C%20who%20said%20he%20was%20not%20getting%20the%2025%25%20pension%20he%20was%20entitled%20to%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%2C%20an%20assistant%20commissioner%20of%20police%2C%2013%20years%20ago.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20voiced%20his%20grievance%20at%20various%20levels%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20engineering%20graduate%20Methri%20Das%20from%20Narayankhed%20said%20his%20loan%20application%20to%20the%20government%20to%20buy%20a%20car%20for%20making%20a%20living%20was%20repeatedly%20rejected%20for%2010%20years.%20An%20autorickshaw%20driver%20from%20Charminar%2C%20Sharafat%20Hussain%2C%20said%20he%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20support%20his%20family%20which%20included%2C%20his%20wife%2C%20three%20sons%20aged%20four%20to%20eight%20years%2C%20his%20aged%20mother%20and%20a%20visually%20challenged%20sister.%20He%20wanted%20financial%20help%20to%20buy%20an%20autorickshaw.%20He%20earned%20about%20Rs%20400%20a%20day%20now%20on%20a%20hired%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20hundreds%20of%20unemployed%20youth%2C%20infirm%20people%2C%20widows%2C%20and%20disabled%20persons%20seeking%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20redressal%20of%20public%20grievances%20through%20such%20congregations%20was%20introduced%20by%20late%20chief%20minister%20Y.%20S.%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy%20and%20continued%20later%20by%20his%20successor%20and%20Congress%20leader%20N.%20Kiran%20Kumar%20Reddy.%20KCR%2C%20however%2C%20made%20no%20such%20attempt%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%20His%20son%20and%20former%20minister%20K.%20T.%20Rama%20Rao%20justified%20it%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20systemic%20failure%20if%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20to%20go%20to%20the%20public%20to%20hear%20grievances%20on%20ration%20cards%20or%20pensions.%E2%80%9D%20It%20could%20be%20settled%20at%20an%20official%20level%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20removed%20the%20long%20iron%20meshing%20which%20was%20used%20as%20a%20barricade%20to%20ward%20off%20protestors%20on%20the%20main%20thoroughfare%20near%20the%20complex.%20The%20security%20cover%20was%20now%20limited%20to%20regulating%20traffic%20in%20view%20of%20the%20surging%20crowd%20of%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%