%20of%20aligning%20a%20brand%20with%20social%20causes%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20strategic%20marketing%20for%20business%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fanti-woke-beer-company-launches-real-women-of-america-calendar%2Farticleshow%2F105841596.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ethics%20Panel%20Member%20On%20The%20Big%20Charge%20Against%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra's%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bunethical%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20got%20someone%20to%20use%20her%20parliament%20login%20credentials%2047%20times%20(sometimes%20from%20Dubai%20and%20America)%2C%20Parliament%20Ethics%20Committee%20Member%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%20told%20NDTV%20on%20the%20day%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20was%20expelled%20from%20parliament%20over%20'cash%20for%20query'%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusinessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20had%20claimed%20in%20a%20signed%20affidavit%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20targeted%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani%20to%20%26quot%3Bmalign%20and%20embarrass%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%2049%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20in%20the%20'cash%20for%20query'%20that%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20conduct%20was%20unethical.%20And%20she%20has%20been%20punished%20for%20the%20same%20by%20parliament.%20It's%20not%20like%20she%20has%20been%20punished%20by%20a%20person%20or%20two.%20The%20matter%20went%20to%20the%20parliament%20standing%20committee%3B%20complainant%20and%20defendant%20were%20heard.%20She%20was%20given%20time%20to%20put%20her%20point%20forward.%20When%20she%20appeared%20before%20the%20committee%2C%20she%20was%20very%20angry%20and%20she%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20unparliamentary%20things%2C%20even%20against%20the%20committee%20chairman%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Aparajita%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20big%20charge%20against%20the%20MP%2C%20she%20said%20her%20parliament%20login%20credentials%20were%20used%20by%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20got%20someone%20to%20use%20her%20parliament%20login%20credentials%2047%20times.%20She%20did%20not%20use%20it%20but%20got%20someone%20to%20use%20it.%20Questions%20were%20uploaded%20from%20Dubai%2C%20America%2C%20Bangalore%20and%20Delhi.%20It%20points%20to%20improper%20behaviour.%20And%20because%20of%20this%20we%20suggested%20her%20expulsion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ms%20Aparajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%2C%20she%20said%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20and%20then%20it%20was%20tabled%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...This%20House%20accepts%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20Committee%20that%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20conduct%20was%20immoral%20and%20indecent%20as%20an%20MP.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate%20for%20her%20to%20continue%20as%20an%20MP...%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20maintains%20that%20the%20Ethics%20committee%20broke%20every%20rule%20and%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bkangaroo%20court%20punished%20me%20without%20evidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEntire%20case%20against%20me%20based%20on%20sharing%20of%20login%20details%2C%20but%20no%20rules%20govern%20this%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20adding%20that%20MPs%20are%20like%20conveyor%20belts%20to%20bring%20questions%20from%20general%20public%20to%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20evidence%20of%20cash%20or%20gift%2C%20ethics%20panel%20decided%20to%20hang%20me%20without%20getting%20to%20root%20of%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20has%20described%20the%20action%20against%20its%20MP%20as%20%26quot%3Bover%20activeness%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20display%20of%20the%20BJP's%20use%20of%20its%20brute%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Aparajita%20said%20the%20MP's%20expulsion%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20make%20us%20happy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20do%20it%20because%20parliament's%20prestige%20was%20at%20stake...%20that's%20why%20we%20had%20to%20do%20it.%20And%20at%20some%20level%2C%20it%20is%20also%20a%20lesson%20for%20us%20parliamentarians%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20there%20is%20need%20for%20a%20separate%20investigation%2C%20Ms%20Aparajita%20said%2C%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%20parliament%2C%20which%20is%20supreme%2C%20has%20decided%2C%20I%20don't%20see%20a%20reason%20for%20any%20other%20agency%20to%20probe%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702034280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fd46mormk_aprajita-sarangi-1200-_625x300_08_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fethics-panel-member-on-the-big-charge-against-mahua-moitra-4646009%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra's%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bunethical%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20got%20someone%20to%20use%20her%20parliament%20login%20credentials%2047%20times%20(sometimes%20from%20Dubai%20and%20America)%2C%20Parliament%20Ethics%20Committee%20Member%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fethics-panel-member-on-the-big-charge-against-mahua-moitra-4646009%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fethics-panel-member-on-the-big-charge-against-mahua-moitra-4646009%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fethics-panel-member-on-the-big-charge-against-mahua-moitra-4646009%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Students%20save%20mother%20and