0that%20his%20family%20went%20through%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20at%20all%20at%20fault%20here.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20straight%20away.%20What%20Mr%20Gauti%20has%20done%2C%20sooner%20or%20later%20all%20of%20you%20will%20get%20to%20know.%20The%20words%20which%20he%20used%20and%20the%20things%20he%20said%20on%20a%20cricket%20field%2C%20live%2C%20is%20not%20acceptable.%20My%20family%2C%20my%20state%2C%20everybody%20has%20gone%20through%20so%20much.%20I%20fought%20that%20battle%20with%20all%20your%20support.%20Now%20people%20want%20to%20down%20me%20for%20no%20reason.%20He%20said%20things%20he%20shouldn't%20have%20said.%20I%20will%20surely%20let%20you%20know%20what%20he%20said%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreesanth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702033980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fl7pg8u7o_gambhir-sreesanth_625x300_07_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sreesanth-spat-new-video-shows-what-exactly-happened-how-teammates-separated-stars-watch-4641972%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Sreesanth%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20heated%20argument%20during%20a%20Legends%20League%20Cricket%20(LLC)%20match%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sreesanth-spat-new-video-shows-what-exactly-happened-how-teammates-separated-stars-watch-4641972%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sreesanth-spat-new-video-shows-what-exactly-happened-how-teammates-separated-stars-watch-4641972%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sreesanth-spat-new-video-shows-what-exactly-happened-how-teammates-separated-stars-watch-4641972%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'We%20do%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20house%20to%20ca