%26quot%3BMahua%20Will%20Win%20Battle%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Condemns%20Trinamool%20MP's%20Expulsion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20condemned%20the%20expulsion%20of%20her%20party%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20blatant%20act%20of%20%26quot%3Bvendetta%20politics%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%2C%2049%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20following%20an%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20held%20her%20guilty%20of%20taking%20bribes%20in%20exchange%20for%20criticising%20the%20government.%20The%20Trinamool%20leader%20faces%20accusations%20of%20receiving%20cash%20and%20luxurious%20gifts%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20posing%20questions%20in%20Parliament%20that%20painted%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20government%20in%20a%20negative%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20vendetta%20politics%20of%20BJP.%20They%20killed%20democracy....It%20is%20injustice.%20Mahua%20will%20win%20the%20battle.%20The%20people%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20the%20BJP.%20They%20will%20be%20defeated%20in%20the%20next%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee%20said%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20shame%20for%20parliamentary%20democracy.%20We%20condemn%20the%20way%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20expelled%2C%20the%20party%20stands%20with%20her.%20They%20(the%20BJP)%20can't%20defeat%20us%20in%20the%20election%2C%20so%20they%20have%20resorted%20to%20vendetta%20politics.%20It%20is%20a%20sad%20day%20and%20the%20betrayal%20of%20Indian%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20denied%20Ms%20Moitra%20the%20opportunity%20to%20defend%20herself%20against%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20(Ms%