the%20Land%20and%20Development%20Office%20(L%26amp%3BDO)%20allegedly%20flouted%20several%20protocols%20while%20carrying%20out%20the%20demolition.%20The%202015%20policy%20mandates%20that%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20must%20be%20provided%2015%20days%20prior%20to%20demolition.%20Pyare%20Lal%20(52)%2C%20a%20resident%20who%20works%20as%20a%20scrap%20dealer%2C%20said%20that%20notices%20announcing%20the%20demolition%20were%20pasted%20only%20three%20days%20earlier%2C%20i.e.%20on%20November%2018.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20the%20notice%20sent%20us%20into%20panic%2C%20then%20we%20heard%20rumours%20that%20the%20demolition%20would%20be%20stayed.%20And%20then%20suddenly%20the%20bulldozers%20came.%20We%20had%20no%20time%20to%20find%20a%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08125316%2FSR-3-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688270%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EResidents%20and%20policemen%20look%20on%2C%20each%20with%20different%20emotions%2C%20as%20the%20bulldozers%20wreak%20havoc%20on%20the%20basti.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20residents%20added%20that%20they%20did%20not%20possess%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20rent%20accommodation%20at%20such%20short%20notice.%20A%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20daily-wage%20earners%2C%20domestic%20workers%20and%20scrap%20collectors.%20The%20DUSIB%20has%20failed%20to%20provide%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20to%20even%20a%20single%20displaced%20family.%20The%20policy%20also%20mentions%20that%20alternate%20rehabilitation%20must%20be%20provided%20within%20five%20kilometres%20from%20the%20site%20of%20a%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegularity%20of%20livelihood%20and%20education%20are%20crucial%20to%20the%20displaced%20families%20of%20Sunder%20Nagar.%20Nasira%20Bibi%20(33)%20works%20as%20a%20domestic%20worker%20in%20a%20posh%20bungalow%20nearby.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20move%20far%20away%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20continue%20working%2C%20and%20I%20was%20earning%20decent%20money%20here.%E2%80%9D%20Her%20children%20study%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Public%20School%2C%20Mathura%20Road%2C%20which%20is%20around%20the%20corner.%20%E2%80%9CI%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20choose%20between%20them%20losing%20a%20year%2C%20and%20paying%20increased%20travel%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130228%2FSR4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130228%2FSR4.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130228%2FSR4-300x224.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Raj%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%2C%20cleared%20out%20possessions%20like%20the%20TV%20and%20the%20water%20filter%20from%20the%20house%20into%20his%20garden.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20also%20states%20that%20demolitions%20cannot%20be%20carried%20out%20while%20school%20and%20college%20examinations%20are%20taking%20place.%20Falak%20(17)%2C%20is%20a%2012th%20standard%20student%2C%20whose%20pre-board%20exams%20are%20due%20next%20month.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20weekly%20practice-test%20tomorrow.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20I%20can%20study%20today%2C%20I%20have%20no%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20At%20the%20demolition%20site%2C%20it%20was%20common%20to%20see%20children%20wearing%20their%20school%20uniform.%20Priya%20(38)%20wiped%20her%20tears%20with%20her%20%3Cem%3Edupatta%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20pointed%20towards%20her%20son%20rummaging%20through%20the%20rubble.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20poor%20boy%20did%20not%20get%20time%20to%20even%20change%20clothes%20or%20eat%20lunch.%20What%20consolation%20could%20I%20possibly%20offer%20him%3F%20His%20future%2C%20all%20our%20futures%20seem%20bleak%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20Chandni%20(14)%20echoed%20a%20similar%20sentiment.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20is%20saying%20that%20we%20will%20go%20back%20to%20our%20village%20after%20my%20final%20exam%E2%80%A6%20and%20you%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20there%E2%80%A6%20I%20will%20have%20to%20quit%20my%20studies%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20relatives%20will%20get%20me%20married%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5.jpg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08130954%2FSR5-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20child%E2%80%99s%20cot%20lies%20empty%20in%20a%20house%20that%20was%20due%20to%20be%20demolished%20the%20next%20day.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Roy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3