rious%20locations%20of%20a%20business%20group%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20Sahu%2C%20as%20he%20attacked%20the%20opposition%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCountrymen%20should%20look%20at%20these%20piles%20of%20currency%20notes%20and%20then%20hear%20the%20addresses%20of%20its%20(Congress)%20leaders%20on%20honesty.%20Every%20penny%20looted%20from%20people%20will%20have%20to%20be%20returned.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20with%20several%20emojis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sahu's%20staff%20expressed%20their%20inability%20to%20get%20a%20comment%20from%20the%20MP%20when%20PTI%20called%20on%20his%20phone%20for%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20I-T%20department's%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20the%20taxman%20acted%20on%20%26quot%3Binputs%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20cash%20being%20remitted%20by%20liquor%20distributors%2C%20sellers%20and%20business%20groups%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20raids%20were%20launched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702032240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpbm5q258_income-tax-raids-odisha-pti-_625x300_08_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-rs-200-crore-recovered-in-income-tax-raids-in-odisha-4645891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnaccounted%26quot%3B%20cash%20amounting%20to%20around%20Rs%20250%20crore%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20recovered%20through%20searches%20being%20conducted%20by%20the%20income-tax%20department%20against%20a%20Odisha-based%20distillery%20group%20and%20entities%20linked%20to%20it%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F