p%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20expelled%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20following%20an%20Ethics%20Committee%20report%20held%20her%20guilty%20of%20taking%20bribes%20in%20exchange%20for%20criticising%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%20MP%20faces%20accusations%20of%20receiving%20cash%20and%20luxurious%20gifts%20from%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20posing%20questions%20in%20Parliament%20that%20painted%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%20a%20negative%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%20Of%20The%20'Cash%20For%20Query'%20Case%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20It%20Began%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2014%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20forwarded%20a%20copy%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20seeking%20to%20address%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20denied%20all%20allegations%20against%20her%2C%20dismissing%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex.%26quot%3B%20In%20response%2C%20Mr%20Dehadrai%20wrote%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20claiming%20he%20feared%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20serious%20threat%20to%20his%20life%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20his%20complaint%20and%20alleging%20a%20direct%20attempt%20to%20coerce%20him%20into%20retracting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20requested%20the%20immediate%20suspension%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20Mr%20Birla.%20Mr%20Dubey%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20accepted%20bribes%20from%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20in%20exchange%20for%20asking%20parliamentary%20questions%20critical%20of%20PM%20Modi%20and%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20These%20actions%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Dubey%2C%20constituted%20breaches%20of%20parliamentary%20privilege%2C%20contempt%20of%20the%20House%2C%20and%20potentially%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey's%20complaint%20triggered%20a%20hearing%20by%20the%20Ethics%20Panel%20of%20Parliament%2C%20summoning%20both%20him%20and%20Mr%20Dehadrai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDarshan%20Hiranandani's%20Explosive%20Claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hiranandani%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20submitted%20an%20affidavit%20alleging%20Ms%20Moitra%20shared%20her%20parliamentary%20credentials%20with%20him%20to%20facilitate%20the%20framing%20and%20posting%20of%20questions%20targeting%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20a%20measure%20she%20perceived%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20reach%20PM%20Modi.%20He%20admitted%20that%20he%20used%20the%20Trinamool%20MP's%20parliamentary%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20post%20questions%20from%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fafhg991o_mahua-moitra-ani-_625x300_08_December_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20ANI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20conceded%20to%20sharing%20her%20parliamentary%20login%20credentials%20with%20Mr%20Hiranandani.%20While%20acknowledging%20a%20receipt%20of%20gifts%20from%20him%2C%20she%20clarified%20that%20they%20were%20limited%20to%20personal%20items%20like%20%26quot%3Bone%20scarf%2C%20some%20lipsticks%2C%20and%20other%20makeup%20items%20including%20eye%20shadow.%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Moitra%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20any%20bribery%20and%20demanded%20the%20opportunity%20to%20cross-examine%20the%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMahua%20Moitra's%20Defiance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20defied%20the%20Ethics%20Committee's%20initial%20summons%20to%20appear%20on%20October%2031.%20She