aim%20that%20the%20incidents%20of%20terrorism%20have%20drastically%20reduced%20and%20laid%20down%20elaborate%20statistics%20to%20indicate%20all-round%20socio-economic%20development%20in%20the%20union%20territory%2C%20he%20also%20used%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20platform%20to%20attack%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20who%20he%20believes%20was%20responsible%20for%20losing%20control%20over%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20undoing%20multiple%20historical%20wrongs%20or%20blunders%20that%20were%20committed%20during%20various%20Congress%20regimes%2C%20beginning%20from%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crux%20of%20his%20speech%20centred%20around%20a%20single%20point%20%E2%80%93%20that%20Kashmir%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20a%20complete%20transformation%20after%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20as%20the%20move%20allowed%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20initiate%20a%20series%20of%20development%20projects%2C%20from%20hydropower%C2%A0%20and%20irrigation%20projects%20to%20even%20multiplexes%20in%20cities%2C%20as%20the%20Centre%20has%20moved%20to%20implement%20a%20%E2%80%9CZero%20Terror%20Plan%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CComplete%20Domination%20Plan%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20last%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20was%2C%20however%2C%20careful%20in%20his%20words%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20had%20never%20said%20that%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%20will%20end%20terrorism.%20He%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20root%20of%20terrorism%20is%20the%20feeling%20of%20separatism%20which%20has%20arisen%20due%20to%20Article%20370%20and%20with%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20reduction%20in%20separatism%20and%20due%20to%20this%20terrorism%20will%20also%20reduce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20went%20on%20to%20cite%20figures%20that%20curiously%20compared%20incidents%20of%20terrorism%20between%201994%20and%202004%20with%20those%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Modi%20years%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1983311%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C70%25%20reduction%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Any%20subject%20expert%20will%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20comparison%20may%20be%20misplaced%2C%20as%20terrorism%20was%20at%20its%20peak%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20following%20which%20such%20incidents%20have%20been%20largely%20on%20the%20decline%20because%20of%20state%20interventions.%20There%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20any%20direct%20correlation%20between%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20overall%20decline%20in%20incidents%20of%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20question%20is%20whether%20there%20has%20been%20any%20substantial%20fall%20in%20terrorism%20since%202018.%20Both%20official%20and%20non-official%20data%20show%20that%20incidents%20of%20terrorism%20are%20far%20from%20over%2C%20even%20as%20year-wise%20break-ups%20indicate%20a%20zig-zag%20graph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fjammu-and-kashmir%2Fjammu-records-increase-in-terror-activities-post-article-370-abrogation-2654850%5C%22%3EOfficial%20data%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Jammu%20region%20recorded%20an%20uptick%20in%20terror%20activities%2C%20including%20in%20recruitment%20of%20terrorists.%20231%20terrorists%20and%20their%20overground%20workers%20(OGWs)%20were%20arrested%20between%20August%205%2C%202019%20and%20June%2016%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division%20%E2%80%93%20a%2071%25%20increase%20in%20such%20arrests%20if%20compared%20to%20the%20period%20between%20October%2027%2C%202015%20and%20August%204%2C%202019.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%20owing%20to%20IED%20blasts%20increased%20from%20three%20in%202015-19%20to%2011%20in%202019-2023%20%E2%80%93%20again%20almost%20a%2073%25%20jump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20terrorist-initiated%20stand-off%20fire%20and%20hit%20and%20run%20cases%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years%20also%20saw%20a%2043%25%20increase%20%E2%80%93%20from%20four%20before%202019%20to%20seven%20in%202023%20%E2%80%93%20even%20as%20terror%20recruitment%20has%20increased%20almost%2039%25.%20The%20figures%20indicate%20a%20considerable%20resentment%20on%20the%20ground%20following%20the%20dilution%20of%20Article%20370%20that%20may%20explode%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20silver%20lining%20in%20the%20official%20statistics%20on%20the%20Jammu%20division%20was%20that%20the%20casualties%20among%20the%20police%20and%20security%20forces%20showed%20a%2013%25%20decline%20after%20Article%20370%20ceased%20to%20be%20in%20place.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%2029%20personnel%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%2032%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20various%20attacks%20post%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20figures%20stood%20at%2033%20deaths%20and%2042%20injuries%20from%20October%2027%2C%202015%20to%20August%204%2C%202019%2C%20stated%20the%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fterror-incidents-in-jk-declining-since-2018-lowest-in-2023-parliament-told%2Farticleshow%2F105786814.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ein%20his%20response%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20Nityanand%20Rai%20gave%20out%20figures%20that%20indicate%20that%20barring%202023%2C%20the%20last%20few%20years%20have%20seen%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20terror-related%20incidents%2C%20which%20are%20not%20very%20different%20from%20the%20period%20before%20Article%20370%20was%20revoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERai%20said%20that%20the%20reported%20%E2%80%9Cterror-initiated%E2%80%9D%20incidents%20dropped%20to%2041%20until%20November%2015%2C%202023%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20compared%20to%20125%20in%202022%2C%20129%20in%202021%2C%20126%20in%202020%2C%20153%20in%202019%2C%20and%20228%20in%202018.%20The%20number%20of%20encounters%2C%20he%20said%2C%20showed%20a%20similar%20dip%20with%2044%20reported%20incidents%20of%20encounters%20in%202023%20compared%20to%20117%20in%202022%2C%20100%20in%202021%2C%20118%20in%202020%2C%20102%20in%202019%2C%20and%20189%20in%202018.%20Rai%20indicated%20that%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20towards%20terrorism%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20decline%2C%20but%20the%20incidents%20shows%20that%20terror-related%20activities%20are%20far%20from%20over%2C%20and%20the%20picture%20is%20not%20as%20rosy%20as%20the%20Shah%20painted%20it%20out%20to%20be%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20also%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20stone%20pelting%20incident%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202023%2C%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20the%202%2C654%20such%20incidents%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Famp%2Findia%2F99-end-to-stone-pelting-in-jk-60-dip-in-casualties-among-forces-no-explosives-seized-reveals-data-8567236.html%5C%22%3Eother%20official%20sources%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20at%20least%20three%20stone-pelting%20incidents%20were%20reported%20in%202023.%C2%A0%20There%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20massive%20dip%20in%20stone-pelting%20incidents%20in%202023%2C%20but%20that%20does%20not%20take%20away%20from%20the%20fact%20that%202023%20could%20very%20well%20be%20an%20exception%20and%20an%20outcome%20of%20lack%20of%20reported%20incidents.%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20data%2C%20a%20total%20of%20324%20incidents%20of%20stone%20pelting%20were%20registered%20by%20local%20authorities%20in%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%202020.%20Next%20year%2C%20such%20incidents%20saw%20a%20dip%20and%20fell%20to%20179.%20Similarly%2C%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20for%20the%20same%20period%2C%20the%20total%20