tions%2C%20that%20is%20a%20fact%20of%20life.%20Primary%20purpose%20for%20which%20ministers%20go%20is%20official%20business.%20Ministers%20discharge%20their%20official%20responsibility%20fully%20satisfactorily%20and%20it%20is%20visible%20in%20the%20results%20of%20the%20foreign%20policy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaishankar%E2%80%99s%20written%20reply%20also%20highlighted%20the%20visits%20as%20a%20means%20to%20strengthen%20ties%20with%20other%20countries%20and%20serving%20national%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20reply%20also%20stated%20that%20101%20memoranda%20of%20understanding%20had%20been%20signed%20with%20different%20countries%20from%202020%20till%20now%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702022442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30123119%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftradition-for-union-ministers-to-attend-overseas-friends-of-bjp-events-on-official-trips-jaishankar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%2C%20'If%20members%20of%20the%20community%20happen%20to%20belong%20to%20a%20political%20party%20or%20have%20political%20affiliations%2C%20that%20is%20a%20fact%20of%20life.%20Primary%20purpose%20for%20which%20ministers%20go%20is%20official%20business.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftradition-for-union-ministers-to-attend-overseas-friends-of-bjp-events-on-official-trips-jaishankar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'2%20Hours%20to%20Read%20104%20Pages'%3A%20Opposition%20as%20Ethics%20Panel%20Tables%20Report%20on%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20Expulsion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08132548%2FUntitled-design-17.jpg%5C%