g%20the%20pandemic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fuk-health-secretary-hancock-quits-after-being-filmed-kissing-aide%2Fa-58058627%5C%22%3EMatt%20Hancock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20the%20inquiry%20last%20week%20that%20he%20had%20tried%20to%20raise%20the%20alarm%20inside%20the%20government%2C%20saying%20thousands%20of%20lives%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20by%20putting%20the%20country%20into%20lockdown%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier%20than%20the%20eventual%20date%20of%20March%2023%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInevitably%20we%20got%20some%20things%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Johnson%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20took%20personal%20responsibility%20for%20all%20the%20decisions%20made.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20we%20were%20doing%20our%20best%20in%20very%20difficult%20circumstances%E2%80%A6%20we%20underestimated%20the%20scale%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20was%20prime%20minister%20from%202019%20to%202022%2C%C2%A0was%20briefly%20interrupted%20when%20a%20protester%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20inquiry%20room%20in%20London%20after%20refusing%20to%20be%20seated%20during%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20others%20were%20also%20later%20removed%2C%20shouting%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dead%20can%E2%80%99t%20hear%20your%20apologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMissing%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20soaring%20death%20toll%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20arrived%20three%20hours%20early%20for%20the%20hearing%2C%20suggesting%20an%20attempt%C2%A0to%20avoid%20the%20bereaved%20families%2C%20some%20of%C2%A0whom%20assembled%20outside%20Dorland%20House%20in%20west%20London%20throughout%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fuk-covid-deaths-pass-150000-amid-omicron-surge%2Fa-60370443%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20230%2C000%20people%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20contracting%20COVID-19%20in%20the%20UK%20between%20March%202020%20and%20mid-July%202021%2C%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20per%20capita%20tolls%20among%20Western%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaced%20with%20evidence%20by%20inquiry%20counsel%20Hugo%20Keith%20that%20the%20UK%20fared%20worse%20in%20the%20pandemic%20than%20its%20European%20neighbors%2C%20Johnson%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20country%20struggled%20with%20a%20new%20pandemic%E2%80%9D%20while%20noting%20the%20UK%20had%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20elderly%20population%E2%80%9D%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20continent%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%E2%80%99s%20grilling%20began%20with%20questions%20about%20a%20failure%20to%20provide%20about%205%2C000%20WhatsApp%20messages%20on%20his%20phone%20from%20late%20January%202020%20to%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20exact%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%20the%20app%20had%20%E2%80%9Csomehow%E2%80%9D%20automatically%20erased%20its%20chat%20history%20from%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20initiated%20a%20so-called%20factory%20reset%20of%20a%20mobile%20device%2C%20Johnson%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20any%20such%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJohnson%20%E2%80%98bamboozled%E2%80%99%20by%20data%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20COVID-19%20inquiry%20in%20late%202021%20following%20pressure%20from%20the%20families%20of%20the%20bereaved%2C%20was%20accused%20by%20former%20aides%20of%20indecisiveness%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20scientific%20understanding%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20former%20chief%20scientific%20officer%2C%20Patrick%20Vallance%2C%20said%20Johnson%20was%20frequently%20%E2%80%9Cbamboozled%E2%80%9D%20by%20scientific%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%E2%80%99s%20former%20adviser%20Dominic%20Cummings%2C%20now%20a%20fierce%20opponent%20of%20Johnson%2C%20said%20the%20then-prime%20minister%20asked%20sci